      <hr class="featurette-divider" />

      <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-7">
          <h2 class="featurette-heading lh-1">Late-Century Churnin' and Burnin'</h2>
          <p class="lead">In the 1970s, the company further diversified, hauling paper starting in 1974 and insulating materials from 1972 to 1980. John S. Wenberg, the grandson of the founder, joined the business in 1967, marking the beginning of the third generation’s leadership. A devastating fire in 1984 destroyed the Wenberg Transfer building, but thanks to the generosity of Shannon’s, the company was able to continue operations by using their facility.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5">
          <div id="carousel3" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
            <div class="carousel-inner featurette-carousel">
              <% carousel3Images.forEach((image, index) => { %>
