      <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
          <h2 class="featurette-heading lh-1">Present-Day Persistence</h2>
          <p class="lead">In 1991, the fourth generation, Clayton Wenberg, joined the company, continuing the family legacy. Over the years, Wenberg Transfer has hauled over 40,000 loads of paper and traveled more than 24 million miles, serving major clients like Boise Cascade and PCA. Though the company ceased international shipping in 2012, it remains a trusted name in hauling paper products across Minnesota.</p>
        </div>
